CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.The plaque is inscribed to "Mayor David L. Lawrence....from the Democrats for United Action, 1937."
TitMainTitle: Copy of a photograph of David L. Lawrence  holding plaque with man wearing bow tie, surrounded by other men and a woman, with a large poster of Lawrence in background
